body:
Hello everyone, for all of those that are unaware, this skin was revealed yesterday :
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sPmjS9ZkX-k
It&#039;s a chinese new year skin for {{champion:254}} Vi, it comes in the Warring kingdoms series along with a skin for {{champion:86}} Garen and {{champion:268}} Azir, keep up with two old ones: {{champion:55}} Kata and {{champion:76}} Nida; and as you can see from the vid, it features small sound changes, mostly on W and R and minor twicks on Q and E, diferent animations on all abilities in a jade green tone ( i&#039;m sorry for the language but it looks like vomit in my opinion), and overall, its a 1350 skin (in my opinion its only worth 975, and i&#039;m not counting the fact that i personally dislike it), however, i&#039;m not here to complain about it, i&#039;m actually ehre to give an idea when i frist saw the splash art- Firecracker Vi, the firecracker is also a new year skin series, in which we have {{champion:42}} Corky and Jinx{{champion:222}} , not only would {{champion:254}} Vi share a theme with her crazy sister, but it would perfectly fit her charecter aswell, rather than releasing this new Warring kingdoms Vi skin i would sugest using the same model (maybe only change the color of her gauntleds to red and yellow) for a Firecracker Vi-
 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pYGPrPqE1A4
here is why i&#039;d say it would look better: 
for animations, the recall could stay the same, maybe just change the small impact partical;
 the Q while charging would make a burning rope sound (like the one for explosives or fireworks);
the W could just change the cross to yellow and the shield to red and then make a firework explosion sound;
the E could create sparkles like the ones we see in the skies in the festivals;
and the R, well, {{champion:254}} Vi&#039;s ult is pretty explosive, the Firecracker theme is explosive, so i&#039;ll let you figure out how it would look like, there are so many ways it would look cool.
So, what do you think? Are you hyped for Warring Kingdoms Vi? wouldn&#039;t you prefer a Firecracker Vi? I would suggest riot to show the idea of what they already have and this idea i&#039;m trying to get out.
Please leave your comments, upvote or downvote this post in the top corner, the more attetion this post gets, the more likelly it will call riot&#039;s attetion, if it doesn&#039;t become popular, well, like all other posts it will be burried and forgotten.
